<bibRefCitation id="EFDEA4C0B674FFCEFDBCB6305741F9EB" author="Kashina, L. I." box="[612,812,1566,1588]" pageId="21" pageNumber="65" pagination="108 - 109" refId="ref15224" refString="Kashina, L. I. (1992) Atraphaxis L. In: Lomonosova, M. N., Bolshakov, N. M. &amp; Krasnoborov, I. M. (Eds.) Flora Sibiriae, vol. 5. Nauka, Sibir. otdel., Novosibirsk, pp. 108 - 109. [in Russian]" type="book chapter" year="1992">Kashina (1992: 109)</bibRefCitation>
